Package: extreme.trawl
Title: Univariate Extreme Values With Trawl Processes
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Valentin",
           family = "Courgeau",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "val.courgeau@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7423-0090"))
Description: Statistical inference tools for univariate extreme time
    series.  It comprises pairwise and generalised method of moments
    inference strategies described in Courgeau and Veraart (2021)
    <doi:10.2139/ssrn.3527739> and simulation schemes based on
    Gamma-distributed trawl processes.
